{"tid":581305,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【食屎啦你】羅致光：基層員工增薪明顯高於通脹　不滿源自期望高","createTime":"2018-03-05T08:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T11:04:01.000Z","uid":38671,"like":3,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"5918b9db52b3d9e0f7a3782fd3e24f093a8bcff4","tid":581305,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180304/s00001/59a6b69bae299a8ca5055d39bb3ed9de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180304%2Fs00001%2F59a6b69bae299a8ca5055d39bb3ed9de.jpg&h=faf553d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n18/19年度財政預算案被批評偏向中產，未有拉近香港貧富差距。勞福局長羅致光認為，解決貧富差距的重點是要令教育更平等、增加就業時上流機會及爭取基層員工合理需求。他指出，過去5年基層員工增薪升幅有明顯增長，甚至高於通脹：「有啲評論話工資追唔到通脹，我覺得唔客觀。當然從感覺好難評論，因為我哋期望都會不斷提升，每一個人都希望生活不斷改善，當你改善嘅速度追唔上期望，就會失望甚至不滿。」<br />\n<br />\n羅致光解釋，在過去幾年，領取最低薪金的基層員工平均每年都有5%至6%的增幅，「薪酬嘅增幅係快過上高個啲架，嗰啲經理嘅增幅係慢」。羅指過往5年薪酬的增幅，較過往25年平均只得0.2%的增幅，有明顯增長。他指，薪酬增幅高於通脹，是從客觀的數字反映。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，香港營商環境中，有98%是中小企，所以在工資增長的承受力會有壓力。"},{"pid":"6f695b0d9e489110709fc02e086cb877f82d137b","tid":581305,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:37:39.000Z","msg":"ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edb620d6004f10273623610b60566bde2f37d1e","tid":581305,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:38:07.000Z","msg":"笑撚死"},{"pid":"c409d648f8